      *          program.
      *
                 INITIALIZE ABNDINFO-REC
                 MOVE EIBRESP    TO ABND-RESPCODE
                 MOVE EIBRESP2   TO ABND-RESP2CODE
      *
      *          Get supplemental information
      *
                 EXEC CICS ASSIGN APPLID(ABND-APPLID)
